title: HP Proliant Servers: Temperature Sensors
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/server/hp
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check connects to the SNMP agent installed on an operating system
 on a HP Proliant server and reads the information from the {CPQHLTH-MIB}
 MIB.
 The systems SNMP agent is extended by the HP Management Agents which need
 to be installed on the monitored systems.

 The check monitors the reported state of the builtin temperature sensors.
 There are no thresholds to be defined in this check. The check uses the
 thresholds reported by the system.

item:
 Index of the temperature sensor followed by the location of the
 sensor in brackets

inventory:
 One service is created for each temperature sensor.
